headline: Fastenal Gears Up to Report Q1 Earnings: Things to Keep in Mind
summary: FAST's Q1 results are likely to reflect manufacturing growth, albeit at a slow pace, with a strong digital strategy and a balanced onsite/offsite mix. Yet, soft industrial markets are concerning.
